@startuml sequence_reset
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Admin Resets Draws — Entry Window Reopens

actor Admin
participant "Admin SPA" as UI
participant "Express API" as API
participant "resetDraws()" as RESET
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

note over DB: Raffle active\ndrawnCount = 2\n(entries closed)

Admin -> UI: Clicks "Reset Draws"
UI -> API: POST /api/admin/raffles/:id/reset
API -> RESET: resetDraws(id)
RESET -> DB: UPDATE participants\nSET is_drawn=false,\ndrawn_at=NULL,\ndraw_order=NULL\nWHERE raffle_id=:id
DB --> RESET: 2 rows updated
RESET --> API: updated raffle
API --> UI: 200 { raffle }

note over DB: drawnCount = 0\n**Entry window reopened**

@enduml
